metadata.description: FAT Brands Inc. is a global franchising company that acquires, develops, markets, and manages quick-service, fast-casual, casual dining, and polished casual dining restaurant concepts. Its portfolio includes brands such as Fatburger, Johnny Rockets, Round Table Pizza, Marble Slab Creamery, and others.
